name: the sleeping planet
description: Since the NFT is a booming market, a group of friends have decided to create this NFT because our goal is to help reduce the climate change that our planet is enduring because of us. For this reason 30% of each sale will be sent to an organization that cares for our planet! This is the first NFT of many to come!!! If you want it to go to a specific organization contact us on twitter @joanmj_photo
